url: "https://github.com/eps-research/rag-corpus-series"
repository-code: "https://github.com/eps-research/rag-corpus-series"
license: CC-BY-4.0
abstract: >
  A unified platform of open astrophysics corpora, cross-epoch kinematic
  analysis tools, LLM-assisted scientific workflows, and educational resources
  spanning Milky Way globular clusters to z~6. Includes four machine-readable
  corpora (438 HI galaxies, 129 dwarfs, 174 globular clusters, 31 high-z
  galaxies) and 120 verified Jupyter notebook examples.
keywords:
  - astrophysics
  - galaxy rotation curves
  - RAG
  - LLM
  - open science
  - high-redshift galaxies
  - globular clusters
